data.text:
Come celebrate the season at Felton Covered Bridge Park! Join us Sunday December 12 from 11am to 3pm for a traditional Holiday Market on the bridge, complete with arts & crafts, delicious food & beverages, music, holiday lights and other festivities.

Great opportunity to get last minute gifts from local artists and to socialize with your neighbors.

Follow the Facebook event at https://www.facebook.com/events/315907816610330.

The Felton Covered Bridge was built in 1892, and is recognized as a historical treasure in the State of California.

Santa Cruz County Parks Department is a sponsor and co-host of the Christmas Market again this year. Learn more about the exceptional public spaces and activities that the #SCParks team provides to Santa Cruz County residents at scparks.com.
